title Tier 5 - Infra and Tool Architecture

direction right

Inputs [icon: inbox, color: teal] {
  Tier 3 Feature Vector [icon: file-text, label: "current behavioural features"]
  Tier 4 Twin Context [icon: user, label: "current + previous snapshots"]
  Optional Events/Simulation [icon: layers, label: "recent typed events + sim hints"]
}

Reasoning Pipeline [icon: cpu, color: purple] {
  Contradiction Stats Engine [icon: bar-chart-2, label: "layer1 z-test\nlayer2 source consistency\nlayer3 LCI"]
  Context Assembler [icon: filter, label: "priority packing + token budgeting"]
  OpenRouter CoT Caller [icon: message-square, label: "structured JSON prompt/response"]
  JSON Validator [icon: check-square, label: "Pydantic parse and schema checks"]
  Deterministic Fallback [icon: shield, label: "threshold-based narrative/flags"]
}

Interrogation Runtime [icon: repeat, color: orange] {
  URS Ranker [icon: target, label: "uncertainty reduction score"]
  Question Template Engine [icon: help-circle, label: "income/expense/commitment/assets/intent"]
  Session State Machine [icon: git-merge, label: "IDLE..COMPLETE/ABANDONED"]
  Answer Parser [icon: tool, label: "regex extraction + patch hints"]
}

Outputs [icon: send, color: green] {
  Tier5 Result Cache [icon: hard-drive, label: "tier5:result:{user_id}"]
  Reasoning Event Stream [icon: layers, label: "stream:reasoning_events"]
  Interrogation Session Store [icon: database, label: "tier5:interrogation:{session_id}"]
}

Tier 3 Feature Vector --> Contradiction Stats Engine: compute contradiction signals
Tier 4 Twin Context --> Context Assembler: delta packet context
Contradiction Stats Engine --> Context Assembler: priority evidence
Context Assembler --> OpenRouter CoT Caller: structured prompt
OpenRouter CoT Caller --> JSON Validator: parse response
JSON Validator --> Deterministic Fallback: failover path
JSON Validator --> URS Ranker: confidence and hypotheses
URS Ranker --> Question Template Engine: select top questions
Question Template Engine --> Session State Machine: create session
Session State Machine --> Answer Parser: parse user turns
Answer Parser --> Interrogation Session Store: persist session updates
Deterministic Fallback --> Tier5 Result Cache: cache latest result
JSON Validator --> Tier5 Result Cache: cache latest result
Tier5 Result Cache --> Reasoning Event Stream: emit completed/flagged events
